cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.SI 

The paper deals with developing classification algorithms that are fair with respect to sensitive attributes of the data, which is a problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CY (Computers and Society). The paper also deals with optimization problems, which could place it in cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) or cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
